message: Hello Bob, I'm excited to offer you our premium product, which is tailored to meet your specific needs and expectations. Given its high quality and unique features, I believe it would significantly enhance your operations or personal endeavors. I am offering this exceptional product to you at a special introductory price of $12000, which I believe is a fantastic opportunity considering its true value exceeds $15000. I look forward to your consideration and the chance to contribute to your success.
